.TH OLNK 1 "May 2026" "OcarinaLNK" "OcarinaLNK User Commands"
.SH NAME
olnk \- OcarinaLNK linker frontend
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B olnk
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B olnk
is the command-line entry point for OcarinaLNK.
It coordinates configuration, format/machine selection, and linking.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.olnk/bin/olnk
Installed executable.
.TP
.I ~/.olnk/formats
Lua format definitions.
.TP
.I ~/.olnk/machines
Lua machine definitions.
.TP
.I ~/.olnk/scripts
User linker scripts.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR olnkidl (1),
.BR olnkquery (1),
.BR olnk-api (3)
